Cognitive Ritual Clear Thinking Simulator (CRCTS)

A fully functional terminal-based symbolic exploration game

that helps humans practice structured thinking under uncertainty.

 

Author: Darrell Lee Stiltner

Email: leelastiltner@gmail.com

