This terminal program allows the user to input text and explore

symbolic representations of ideas through multiple cognitive zones:

Axis, Tree, Geometry, Fractal, Heart, Pulse, Hexagram, and Fusion.

 

All content and symbolic structures are generated programmatically

to provide a dynamic cognitive ritual experience.

 

Do not remove or alter this header without permission.

